column2: SELECT     z.RAJ AS ra1, z.DEJ AS dec1,z.nu,z.umed,z.s_umag as zue,z.ng,z.gmed,z.s_gmag as zge,z.nr,z.rmed,z.s_rmag as zre,    n.objid, n.distance,   ph.ra AS ra2, ph.dec AS dec2,ph.psfMag_u,ph.psfMagErr_u,ph.psfMag_g, ph.psfMagErr_g, ph.psfMag_r,ph.psfMagErr_r  into mydb.zmatch_badcounts_r from myDB.zeljko AS z    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( z.RAJ, z.DEJ, #) AS n   JOIN PhotoObj AS ph ON n.objid=ph.objid  where ph.type = #      and (ph.flags_r & #) !=#
